Relieved, i then got my bind spell ready and cast it upon me. &quot;Thank you again scaley one, and contact me if you need to pull her out and i will have gate and a circle spell ready to come and get you both out fast and you wont have to run. When this is done, remind me to repay all your kindness and help somehow!&quot; I knelt in revilence and humility to him out of respect.<br>
Returning the gesture of respect, Mythias bowed to me and replied,&quot;Go now and we will be waiting for you. Good fortune my sssoft ssskinned friend!&quot;<br>
With that, i called upon the spirits of the winds and stepped into the comforting blackness that was the &quot;everything&quot;. Mulling over all that was needing to be done i thought of my blood sister, Kaitlyne and her welfare.<br>
Then the rip in space and i was standing before the Druids at the West Commons ring. I quickly asked the spirits to camo me and i was off, racing to Highkeep. It was time to check on Kaitlyne. I reached out for her with my mind and immediatley linked with her. &quot;Kaitlyne my sister, how fair thee? What is Ragingwolf up to?&quot;<br>
