Everyone seemed to calm down and understand her words. Tweani returned with Katreena's spell book in hand. She passed over the table to me and as i grabbed it, Tweani took hold of my hand and she winked as if saying she believed in what Katreena was doing and giving her blessings. I placed her spell book in my backpack and prepared to depart. Standing up from the table i bowed to all and then knelt and kissed Lady Kuvanu's hand. &quot;Thank you M'lady and i love you all!&quot; Lady Kuvanu turned me bak to her and said, &quot;Young Kygero go to Katreena and tell her she has our blessings and that we all love her and pray for her safety! We will be ready when the time comes. No go and be careful, contact us when you have given her the book.&quot;<br>
