&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &quot;Okay Kat do your thing&quot;. Ordered Farvak.  I cast the spells necessary for our travel to the docks of the Overthere.   I couldn't look at Gorsha feeling that I should have died rather than put his life at risk.  So we traveled silently to the Headquarters of the Plague Bringers.  <br>
<br>
