    I spoke my voice calm and almost musical  &quot;Leave, me leave? Free? Whatever makes you think I want to leave? I have all that I want here and now for my purposes.  You seem to miss the point of my actions Iszabelle&quot; her face darkened as we stood together her breath hot against my face. <br>
