         I continued &quot;Yes, I am here to distract and disrupt Farvak and your plans for the Bronze Dragon Fellowship.  But you and I both know that there is something more going on here than the war between the Plague Bringers and the Bronze Dragon Fellowship.  You and I are instruments of our own Gods yours and mine.  I have been prepared for this battle all of my life have you?&quot;  My eyebrow raised to her on this last note. I brushed my hair aside, as blood dripped down my neck, warm and wet.<br>
