<br>
She will not expect this MiLord, Safvas smiled despite itself,  her blood will fuel the return of our kind to the prime material plane!  We will bring hell to Norrath Lord.<br>
--------------------------------------------------<br>
<br>
Darkness: a moment in time before the truth is revealed<br>
